==================================================================================
* ActionScript mode
* Flex specific
* Magic for XML Mode
* GO Mode
* Erlang Emacs Mode -- Configuration End
* EDTS
* TypeScript support
* Apache Pig Latin
* Clojure mode -- using Marmelade
